---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="主题测试">
  <div class="p-8 space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">暗色模式测试</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">测试卡片 1</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">这是一个测试暗色模式的卡片。点击右上角的主题切换按钮来切换浅色/深色主题。</p>
        <button class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg transition-colors">
          测试按钮
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">测试卡片 2</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">另一个测试卡片，验证暗色模式下的样式表现。</p>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
            <div class="bg-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full w-3/4"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
            <div class="bg-green-600 h-2 rounded-full w-1/2"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white p-6 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">渐变背景测试</h3>
      <p>这个区域使用渐变背景，在深色模式下应该保持不变。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>